<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>
        <%= title %>
    </title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/style.css">
</head>

<body>
    <%- include('../partials/school_header') %>
        <main>
            <section class="page-header" style="background-image: url('/images/school-hero.png');">
                <div class="container">
                    <h1>Academic Excellence</h1>
                    <p>A curriculum designed to inspire curiosity, creativity, and critical thinking.</p>
                </div>
            </section>

            <section class="content-section">
                <div class="container">
                    <div class="row" style="display: flex; gap: 40px; flex-wrap: wrap;">
                        <div style="flex: 2; min-width: 300px;">
                            <h2>Comprehensive Curriculum</h2>
                            <p>At N.R.K. Public School, we follow the Central Board of Secondary Education (CBSE)
                                curriculum, enriched with innovative teaching methodologies. Our academic program is
                                designed to provide a balanced mix of rigid academic discipline and free-flowing
                                creative expression.</p>

                            <div class="academic-levels" style="margin-top: 30px;">
                                <div style="margin-bottom: 30px;">
                                    <h3 style="color: var(--primary-blue);">Primary Wing (Grades 1-5)</h3>
                                    <p>Focus on foundation building, language skills, and basic mathematical concepts
                                        through activity-based learning.</p>
                                </div>
                                <div style="margin-bottom: 30px;">
                                    <h3 style="color: var(--primary-blue);">Middle Wing (Grades 6-8)</h3>
                                    <p>Introduction to specialized subjects, scientific inquiry, and analytical
                                        reasoning. Encouraging independent study habits.</p>
                                </div>
                                <div style="margin-bottom: 30px;">
                                    <h3 style="color: var(--primary-blue);">Secondary Wing (Grades 9-10)</h3>
                                    <p>Rigorous preparation for board examinations with a focus on depth of
                                        understanding and practical application of knowledge.</p>
                                </div>
                            </div>

                            <div style="margin-top: 30px;">
                                <h3>Innovative Teaching</h3>
                                <ul style="list-style: none; padding-left: 0;">
                                    <li style="margin-bottom: 12px; display: flex; align-items: flex-start;"><i
                                            class="fas fa-check text-gold"
                                            style="margin-right: 15px; margin-top: 5px;"></i>
                                        <div><strong>Experienced and Dedicated Faculty:</strong> Our teachers are highly
                                            qualified, passionate, and committed to student success.</div>
                                    </li>
                                </ul>
                            </div>
                        </div>

                        <div style="flex: 1; min-width: 300px;">
                            <div class="feature-card"
                                style="padding: 30px; border-radius: 8px; background: var(--bg-cream); border-top: 4px solid var(--accent-gold);">
                                <h3 style="margin-bottom: 20px;">Beyond Textbooks</h3>
                                <ul style="list-style: none; padding-left: 0;">
                                    <li style="margin-bottom: 15px; display: flex; align-items: center;"><i
                                            class="fas fa-check text-gold" style="margin-right: 10px;"></i> Smart
                                        Classrooms</li>
                                    <li style="margin-bottom: 15px; display: flex; align-items: center;"><i
                                            class="fas fa-check text-gold" style="margin-right: 10px;"></i> Computer
                                        Education</li>
                                    <li style="margin-bottom: 15px; display: flex; align-items: center;"><i
                                            class="fas fa-check text-gold" style="margin-right: 10px;"></i> Science
                                        Olympiads</li>
                                    <li style="margin-bottom: 15px; display: flex; align-items: center;"><i
                                            class="fas fa-check text-gold" style="margin-right: 10px;"></i> Language
                                        Labs</li>
                                </ul>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </section>
        </main>
        <%- include('../partials/footer') %>
</body>

</html>